listDescription: Zero knowledge identity projects that have made significant contributions to the OP ecosystem, including live contracts that empower OP users with private & secure identity. These projects enable import of off-chain credentials on to OP to bridge reputation on-chain.
impactEvaluationDescription: Minimum 1k users, with auditable deployment of zero knowledge proofs and/or circuits. Clear privacy guidelines and requirements. Must have on-chain activity.

projectsMetadata.bio: ZK identity protocol for sybil resistance, secure key custody, and open civics.
